* SonarCloud can easily import pylint and flake8 issues in case you want to use a rule SonarCloud does not already provide. Note however that pylint/flake8 rules and SonarCloud rules are implemented differently. You might see new issues with SonarCloud, or less issues in some cases (we try to avoid False Positives as much as possible).
* SonarCloud is free for open-source projects."
